spec_data.Name: texlive-onlyamsmath
spec_data.Description:
This package inhibits the usage of plain TeX and (on demand) of
standard LaTeX mathematics environments. This is useful for
class writers who want to encourage their users to use the
environments provided by the amsmath package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:15:37 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Inhibit use of non-amsmath mathematics markup when using amsmath
